				  <span class="rearSpacers">
					{vehicleData?.["rear-spacer"]}
				  </span>{" "}
				  spacers in the rear.
				</p>
				<p>
				  With this setup there is{" "}
				  <span class="frontRubbing">
					{vehicleData?.["front-rubbing"]}
				  </span>{" "}
